(rope creaking)
(leaves rustling)

1:00:22.653 --> 1:00:25.420
(camera clicking)

1:00:31.795 --> 1:00:34.796
- tell kelly that I will come
pick you up tomorrow, okay?

1:00:34.898 --> 1:00:37.633
Daddy just needs to
save a few more lives.

1:00:37.735 --> 1:00:38.533
Okay.

1:00:40.037 --> 1:00:43.538
