(dramatic music)

1:01:01.725 --> 1:01:04.259
(gasping)

1:01:07.998 --> 1:01:09.431
- ed! Ed! Ed!

1:01:09.533 --> 1:01:12.200
(gasping)

1:01:14.338 --> 1:01:15.404
- diana.

1:01:15.506 --> 1:01:16.672
I didn't, I didn't
know it was you.

1:01:16.774 --> 1:01:18.306
I didn't.
- Look.

1:01:18.409 --> 1:01:19.474
I'm so sorry.

1:01:19.576 --> 1:01:20.575
I just wanted to
make you some dinner.

1:01:20.678 --> 1:01:23.078
- You look, you
look just like her.

1:01:23.180 --> 1:01:24.513
- I should go.

1:01:24.615 --> 1:01:25.447
- [ed] hey! Hey!

1:01:25.549 --> 1:01:27.582
- Ed, please let go of me.

1:01:29.787 --> 1:01:33.555
(footsteps retreating)

1:01:33.657 --> 1:01:36.692
(ed sighing)

1:01:36.794 --> 1:01:39.428
(phone ringing)

1:01:45.436 --> 1:01:46.668
- what is it?

1:01:46.770 --> 1:01:50.605
(police chatter in background)

1:01:55.679 --> 1:01:59.014
(soft suspenseful music)

1:02:07.057 --> 1:02:07.789
sean.

1:02:07.891 --> 1:02:08.757
- Hmm?

1:02:09.626 --> 1:02:10.425
- Hey.

1:02:11.361 --> 1:02:12.594
- Uh.

1:02:12.696 --> 1:02:14.463
All right, so listen.

1:02:16.066 --> 1:02:17.833
Have you been drinking?

1:02:17.935 --> 1:02:19.568
- I'm just, I'm
just tired, sean.

1:02:19.670 --> 1:02:21.069
- Okay.

1:02:21.171 --> 1:02:21.870
Um.

1:02:21.972 --> 1:02:22.771
- Dr. Thompson.

1:02:22.873 --> 1:02:24.973
Um, why don't we go upstairs?

1:02:25.909 --> 1:02:27.042
- Yeah, come on.

1:02:27.144 --> 1:02:28.076
- What is this?

1:02:31.315 --> 1:02:32.948
- Ed, someone sent
in some photos.

1:02:40.924 --> 1:02:43.358
- Is that the tattoo you
told us your wife has

1:02:43.460 --> 1:02:45.026
when you gave us a description?

1:02:46.497 --> 1:02:48.396
- Who sent this?

1:02:48.499 --> 1:02:51.767
- The number couldn't be
traced, but we're workin' on it.

1:02:51.869 --> 1:02:54.202
- Ed, we need you to
confirm it with us.

1:02:54.304 --> 1:02:55.403
Is that jade's tattoo?

1:02:57.374 --> 1:03:00.742
(soft suspenseful music)

1:03:03.547 --> 1:03:04.346
- yeah.

1:03:11.989 --> 1:03:12.954
There are more?

1:03:15.993 --> 1:03:16.825
- A few.

1:03:18.128 --> 1:03:19.161
- [ed] show me.

1:03:19.263 --> 1:03:20.295
- Oh, come on, ed,
that's not a good idea.

1:03:20.397 --> 1:03:23.865
- Show me!
(hand thumping)

1:03:23.967 --> 1:03:27.035
(soft dramatic music)

1:03:37.748 --> 1:03:40.415
- based on your identification
and these images,

1:03:40.517 --> 1:03:43.852
it's likely we won't
find her alive.

