1:23:17.693 --> 1:23:19.460
- Where did you go, mommy?

1:23:19.562 --> 1:23:21.595
- When you get a
little bit older,

1:23:21.697 --> 1:23:23.931
I can tell you why I had to go.

1:23:24.033 --> 1:23:25.199
- [kayla] okay.

1:23:25.301 --> 1:23:26.834
- And the best part is
you don't have to see

1:23:26.936 --> 1:23:28.435
mommy cry anymore.

1:23:29.672 --> 1:23:30.437
- Okay.

1:23:36.479 --> 1:23:41.749
- Okay, so I think that we
should go to the park

1:23:41.851 --> 1:23:42.983
and we should get
some ice cream.

1:23:43.085 --> 1:23:45.386
So, what kind of ice cream
do you want?

1:23:45.488 --> 1:23:49.523
- [all] strawberry!
(laughing)

1:23:49.625 --> 1:23:52.359
(uplifting music)
